long_description:
About Athletiq

A home-grown sportswear brand to keep you comfortable and look your best while you work hard at the gym. A blend of athleisure and casual wear, Athletiq products range from fashion to sports goods, with highest quality you can trust. Gear up for your next work-out session with confidence and style as you select your favorites from the wide range available with this brand.


Made for those who wish to perfect the athleisure look, this brand brings to you casual and performance clothing with a sporty look. Every trendsetter’s choice, Athletiq is the ideal blend of fashion and comfort. Select from the wide range of biker shorts to lightweight jackets, casual tees, and everyday joggers.

 

Constructed with seamless technology and lightweight, stretchable fabric these products are what you need to make your workouts more comfortable.

 

Features: Seamless construction prevents chafing. Stretchable jacquard fabric allows easy 360 degree movement

long_description:
About Athletiq

A home-grown sportswear brand to keep you comfortable and look your best while you work hard at the gym. A blend of athleisure and casual wear, Athletiq products range from fashion to sports goods, with highest quality you can trust. Gear up for your next work-out session with confidence and style as you select your favorites from the wide range available with this brand.


Made for those who wish to perfect the athleisure look, this brand brings to you casual and performance clothing with a sporty look. Every trendsetter’s choice, Athletiq is the ideal blend of fashion and comfort. Select from the wide range of biker shorts to lightweight jackets, casual tees, and everyday joggers.

 

Constructed with seamless technology and lightweight, stretchable fabric these products are what you need to make your workouts more comfortable.

 

Features: Seamless construction prevents chafing. Stretchable jacquard fabric allows easy 360 degree movement

long_description:
- Easy to go and store. No need to go buy a yoga carrying strap. We've got you covered. Because we love adding value to you and your practice.

- With double sided non-slip surfaces, yoga mat comes with an excellent slip resistant advantage to prevent injuries

- Exceptional resilience allow you to keep your balance during any exercise style. Moisture resistant technology makes the mat to be easily washed with soap and water
feature_bullets: ['Easy care, yoga mat that meets a wide variety of needs', 'Moisture-resistant skin is easy to clean and extremely durable', 'Boasts enhanced durability with top-quality material', 'The length of our strap is adjustable to carry gym mat easily', 'Eco friendly non slip exercise and fitness mats for workout with carrying strap']
